name: coconut
description: Fast and secure paired programming tool. It has integrated audio notes with an Android Smartphone and Facebook, WhatsApp and Slack Views
readme:
# Coconut Coconut is a paired programming package for Atom. It works fast and secure and it can be used with an Android companion app. The companion app can send audio notes in user's code. [Coconut server repository](https://github.com/alexandruionascu/coconut_server) ![Coconut package demo](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alexandruionascu/coconut/master/coconut_demo.gif)
[Coconut companion repository](https://github.com/alexandruionascu/coconut-companion)
